{
  "stem": "5911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She is also speaking a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We met her, I-- and she told me a story that I didn't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was very pregnant in Bad Gastein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My mother was the nurse in the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The doctor that looked after her was a big, burly German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was deathly afraid of her, and she claims my mother saved her son and saved her life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My mother stood up to this doctor and said-- she had terrible labor-- labor pains.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Terrible, she was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother pushed him away and said, I will look after this woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would, but she says because three weeks later, he was indicted of killing Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That same doctor, this German doctor, this Nazi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she told me on the 50th anniversary, when we met for the weekend of celebrating, because she-- we were together in Bad Gastein.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her brother was my very good friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because don't forget, when we got in Bad Gastein, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all latched-- everybody latched onto somebody else to have a-- a continuity, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody became such good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Families were lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Families were lost.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as I got there in 1945, until '47, we made fantastic friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was there, and her-- she had a husband, and she had a brother, and the husband's brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We became very-- they married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We became very close friends, the two boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right away, immediately.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started again about Yiddish [YIDDISH], about the holidays, and Hebrew a little bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, a Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was my teacher that was the teacher that associated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's retired.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I started an associate, and I saw him, because I went to Montreal, and he went to Toronto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
